sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant L as Agent Loop
  participant T as Tool Runtime
  participant R as Scoped Retrieval
  participant C as Context Policy
  participant M as Model
  participant E as Event Log

  U->>L: Fix test failure
  L->>T: run_test intent
  T-->>L: observation: role undefined
  L->>R: retrieval intent + scope
  R->>R: recall/filter/rerank/snapshot
  R-->>C: evidence block + snapshotId
  C->>M: model input with citations
  M-->>L: read/edit intent
  L->>E: model request references snapshotId
